articles.contents:
Hi, welcome to our group project website for visual analytics. Our group consist of Ting Yen-Hsin, He Qiyun and Ng Jianyuan Caine.
About
This project is about building a visual analytics app to analyze time series trend of sales at a chain of department stores. Please reference to respective sections for detailds.
